ny, many persons calling for a retaliation against Bin Laden for the embassy bombings, to claim it was motivated solely by political expediency is foolish.  As it would have been the height of idiocy for anyone to think that the retaliation against Bin Laden would ever eliminate the Lewinsky scandal, Clinton never would have launched the attack for such a shallow purpose.  Say what you want about the man's ethics, but he was not exactly a fool when it came to PR.<br><br>Don't be small-minded and try and lay the blame on one person in the US.  We've had a policy in the US for a LONG, LONG time that was antagonistic toward Bin Laden's goals, and supportive of his primary enemy, Israel.  It is those policies which are the source of his rage at the US.  And it is those policies which MUST NOT be changed in response to this evil man's actions.  We must not give in! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usetis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Setis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 381<br> <font color=#E9D756>(9/11/01 6:28:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrfrm18.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=148.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: I am in shock.</span><hr size=1> Bush has said we will make no distinction between terrorists and those that harbor them.<br><br> <p><B>Setis Dagre</B><BR><B>Ice Clan</B><BR><I>"Some people like to stand out in the rain without an umbrella.  That's what it means to live free."<BR></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=rig